title: Gelateria Paradiso
description: Gelato shop in historic old town. Offers 6 - 10 vegan flavors each day. Staff does not understand vegan or vegano, so ask which ones are sin leche. Variety of unusal fruits like uva de isabella, zapote, nispero, lulo, guanabana.
streetAddress: Edif. Pombo, Calle de la Estrallla con Calle del Cuartel, Esquina
